@startuml "Ionosense HPC - Memory Management"
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam classBackgroundColor #F0F8FF
skinparam classBorderColor #4169E1
skinparam packageBackgroundColor #E6F3FF
skinparam arrowColor #4169E1

title Ionosense HPC - BatchExecutor Memory Layout (v0.9.4+)
footer IEEE Publication Quality Diagram - © 2025 | Updated: 2025-01-19

note top
  **BatchExecutor Mode**: High-throughput, minimal overhead
  Total Memory: ~164 KB (nfft=2048, channels=2)
end note

package "Host Memory Space" #90EE90 {
  class "Input Buffer\n(float*)" as HostInput {
    size: nfft * channels
    layout: interleaved [ch0, ch1, ...]
  }

  class "Output Buffer\n(float*)" as HostOutput {
    size: (nfft/2+1) * channels * frames
    layout: magnitude spectrum
  }

  class "PinnedHostBuffer[0]\ninput_staging" as Pinned0 <<page-locked>> {
    size: nfft * channels
    purpose: double buffering
  }

  class "PinnedHostBuffer[1]\noutput_staging" as Pinned1 <<page-locked>> {
    size: (nfft/2+1) * channels
    purpose: double buffering
  }
}

package "Device Memory Space" #FFD700 {
  class "DeviceBuffer[0]\nInput" as DevInput0 {
    size: nfft * channels * sizeof(float)
    stride: nfft
    layout: per-channel
  }

  class "DeviceBuffer[1]\nInput" as DevInput1 {
    size: nfft * channels * sizeof(float)
    stride: nfft
    layout: per-channel
  }

  class "DeviceBuffer\nIntermediate" as DevIntermediate {
    size: (nfft/2+1) * channels * sizeof(float2)
    format: complex (R2C output)
    note: Hermitian symmetry
  }

  class "DeviceBuffer\nOutput" as DevOutput {
    size: (nfft/2+1) * channels * sizeof(float)
    format: magnitude
    layout: [ch0_bins, ch1_bins, ...]
  }

  class "Window Coefficients" as WindowCoef <<cached>> {
    size: nfft * sizeof(float)
    precomputed: true
  }

  class "cuFFT Work Area" as WorkArea {
    size: dynamic
    managed by: CufftPlan
  }
}

package "PCIe Transfer" <<Transport>> #FFE4E4 {
  class "H2D Stream[0]" as H2D
  class "D2H Stream[2]" as D2H
}

' Data flow
HostInput --> Pinned0 : memcpy
Pinned0 --> H2D : async
H2D --> DevInput0 : cudaMemcpyAsync

DevInput0 --> DevInput0 : window (in-place)
DevInput0 --> DevIntermediate : FFT (R2C)
DevIntermediate --> DevOutput : magnitude

DevOutput --> D2H : async
D2H --> Pinned1 : cudaMemcpyAsync
Pinned1 --> HostOutput : memcpy

WindowCoef --> DevInput0 : element-wise mult

note right of Pinned0
  **Page-locked memory**
  Enables faster PCIe
  transfers (~25 GB/s)
  cudaHostAlloc()
end note

note bottom of DevIntermediate
  **Complex format**
  Hermitian symmetry
  Only N/2+1 bins stored
  Saves 50% memory
end note

note bottom
  **BatchExecutor Memory Characteristics**:
  - Direct pipeline: H2D → Compute → D2H
  - Minimal overhead: 164 KB (nfft=2048, channels=2)
  - Double buffering for input/output
  - No ring buffers (streaming-only feature)

  **Terminology (v0.9.4)**:
  - **channels** = spatial dimension (independent signal sources)
  - **frames** = temporal dimension (FFT windows over time)
  - **bins** = spectral dimension (frequency components)
end note

@enduml